<p style="margin:0;font-size:0.95em;line-height:1.5;flex:1">The speed specialist. Sonic's <strong>Boost</strong> is faster than Blaze's, making him ideal for ground-level speedruns. He has access to <strong>Homing Attack</strong> (RB) with a visual reticle, Stomp from Colors DS, and Air Boost for mid-air dashes. Tails tags along as a companion during gameplay. His strength lies in chaining boosts through the lower, faster routes.</p>
